title: Ranji Trophy: Virender Sehwag sizzles with 92 as Haryana score 303/6 vs Maharashtra
text:
*Pune:* Virender Sehwag yesterday started the Ranji Trophy season for his new state Haryana in right earnest as his sparkling 92 set the foundation of a decent score of 303 for six at stumps against hosts Maharashtra, here yesterday.
*Virender Sehwag*
